    {
        "content": "<p>Somehow my <code>lake</code> vanished all of a sudden. What might be the issue and how do I get it back? There has got to be a command to install lake, right?</p>\n<p><code>Command 'lake' not found, did you mean:</code></p>",
        "id": 516047430,
        "sender_full_name": "Vasily Ilin",
        "timestamp": 1746378272
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you have it in your path? In linux and macOS it's typically in <code>$HOME/.elan/bin/lake</code>. What OS are you using? i.e. \"are you sure it's uninstalled and not just that you're not finding it\"?</p>",
        "id": 516047676,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1746378458
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also, how did you install <code>elan</code>/<code>lake</code>?</p>",
        "id": 516047804,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1746378549
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"214703\">@Yury G. Kudryashov</span> , using the standard instructions <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/get_started.html\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/get_started.html</a></p>",
        "id": 516047923,
        "sender_full_name": "Vasily Ilin",
        "timestamp": 1746378628
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110038\">@Kevin Buzzard</span> , I don't know, my guess is not, because I am sure I did not uninstall it. It literally worked 20 minutes ago. I am on Linux</p>",
        "id": 516047956,
        "sender_full_name": "Vasily Ilin",
        "timestamp": 1746378661
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>These instructions? <a href=\"https://docs.lean-lang.org/lean4/doc/quickstart.html\">https://docs.lean-lang.org/lean4/doc/quickstart.html</a></p>",
        "id": 516047977,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1746378684
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you have <code>~/.elan/bin</code>?</p>",
        "id": 516047997,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1746378708
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yes.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">base</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">vilin</span><span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"n\">doppio</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"bp\">~/</span><span class=\"n\">lean</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"kn\">class</span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">~/.</span><span class=\"n\">elan</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span>\n<span class=\"n\">elan</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">lake</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">lean</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">leanc</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">leanchecker</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">leanmake</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">leanpkg</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 516048059,
        "sender_full_name": "Vasily Ilin",
        "timestamp": 1746378736
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Solved with </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"kn\">export</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PATH</span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"$HOME/.elan/bin:$PATH\"</span><span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">~/.</span><span class=\"n\">bashrc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&amp;&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">source</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">~/.</span><span class=\"n\">bashrc</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Thanks, <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"214703\">@Yury G. Kudryashov</span> , I just didn't know where to look!</p>",
        "id": 516048306,
        "sender_full_name": "Vasily Ilin",
        "timestamp": 1746378921
